name: extreme_with_shadow_inside_then_branch
section: binding-scope-deep
args: cond:Bool outer:Int inner:Int fallback:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [x {outer}] (= (if {cond} (with [x {inner}] x) {fallback}) (if {cond} {inner} {fallback})))
